Anyways what I'm thinking is real interesting is that this new child of hate, Zerinae D'Tora, is chained to the wall on the bottom level of Befallen. Why?<br>
Me thinks VERY strongly that this is linked to Mayong.<br>
Mayong wants revenge on Innoruk for cursing him in to his present state, no? What better way to do that than to kill his new chosen child of hate. Thus, Lany's has the best trade for Mayong, in order to get her last piece of the Maleovence, the gem. <br>
However, we know that Lany's has taken over Befallen, BUT, she herself cannot even entred as it is blessed with so much hate &quot;It has been so strongly warded that Lanys herself cannot safely enter there. This place is Befallen&quot;<br>
So, how the hell is she gonna use Zerinae D'Tora to her advantage?<br>
Just some new things to think about.<br>
